metadata.name: Home Road [001]
metadata.description:
Home Road is a series of images captured during the summer of 2020 during the COVID-19 pandemic. For many, this was a time of prolonged internal introspection brought on by dystopic external circumstances. The isolative nature of this endeavor lead many to confront their egos, subconsciously re-shaping the way they identify with themselves. 

Both images are featured in my first publication titled 'Shadow Aspect.'
